dct_title_s: Γεωλογικός χάρτης της Ελλάδος : Ν. Αίγινα = Geological map of Greece : Aegina Island / Volker Dietrich, Panagiotis Gaitanakis, Ivan Mercolli. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours at 20-meter intervals and hachures. Map includes present and inferred faults, overthrusts, strike and dip of beds, hydrothermally altered zones, thermal waters, clay deposits. Verso includes "Neotectonic map of the Saronic Gulf." Table and"Volcanic evolution of Aegina Island." "Publication by Stiftung Vulkaninstitut Immanuel Friedlaender at the Institute for Mineralogy and Petrography, Federal Institute of Technology, Zurich Switzerland."
dct_publisher_sm: Zürich, Switzerland : Institute for Mineralogy and Petrography, Federal Institute of Technology, 1991.
